#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: blfs-en/postlfs/filesystems/uefi-bootloaders/grub-setup.xml:289
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "In these cases, follow this section to install GRUB EFI application into the"
