#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: blfs-en/postlfs/filesystems/uefi-bootloaders/grub-setup.xml:296
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "To install GRUB with the EFI application installed into the hardcoded path "
