#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: blfs-en/postlfs/filesystems/uefi-bootloaders/grub-setup.xml:324
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The EFI firmware usually prefers the EFI applications with the path recorded"
