msgid ""
"Issue the <command>efibootmgr | cut -f 1</command> command to recheck the "
"EFI boot configuration.  An example of the output is:"
msgstr ""
"Tapez <command>efibootmgr | cut -f 1</command> pour revérifier la "
"configuration de démarrage EFI. Voici un exemple de sortie&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
